This article is a Presidential Memorandum issued by President Donald J. Trump on July 22, 2019. The memorandum is addressed to the Secretary of Defense and discusses a Presidential Determination pursuant to Section 303 of the Defense Production Act of 1950, as amended. The President determines that the domestic production capability for Samarium Cobalt Rare Earth Permanent Magnets is essential to national defense. The President states that without Presidential action, the United States industry cannot adequately and timely provide the production capability for these magnets. The memorandum authorizes and directs the publication of this memorandum in the Federal Register.